{%- comment -%}
  Section: pricing-section
  Type: product_info
  Generated by: Section Conversion Agent v1.2
  Dawn version: 15.0
  Note: The HTML snippet provided contains a centered brand logo image banner.
  Content signals (pricing options, ATC button, shipping info) were not present
  in the actual HTML. This section faithfully converts the provided markup.
  IMAGE UPLOAD REQUIRED: Merchants must upload the brand logo via Theme Editor
  (Settings > Logo image).
